quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  28,61,Kiya woh shaks jiss say hum ney nek wada kiya hai jissay woh qata’an paney wala hai misil uss shaks kay ho sakta hai? Jissay hum ney zindaganiy-e-duniya ki kuch yun hi si manfa’at dey di phir bil-aakhir woh qayamat kay roz pakra baandha hazir kiya jayega
  28,62,Aur jiss din Allah Taalaa unhen pukar ker farmaye ga kay tum jinehn apnay gumaan mein mera shareek thera rahey thay kahan hain
  28,63,Jin per baat aa chuki woh jawab den gay kay aey humaray perwerdigar! Yehi woh hain jinhen hum ney behka rakha tha hum ney enhen issi tarah behkaya jiss tarah hum behkay thay hum teri sarkar mein apni dast darazi kertay hain yeh humari ibadat nahi kertay thay
  28,64,Kaha jayega apnay shareekon ko bulao woh bulayen gay lekin woh jawab tak na den gay aur sab azab dekh len gay kaash yeh log hidayat paa letay
  28,65,Uss din unn ko bula ker poochay ga kay tum ney nabiyon ko kiya jawab diya
  28,66,Phir uss din unn ki tamam daleelen gumm hojayen gi aur aik doosray say sawal tak na keren gay
  28,67,Haan jo shaks tauba ker ley eman ley aaye aur nek kaam keray yaqeen hai kay woh nijat paaney walon mein say hojaye ga
  28,68,Aur aap ka rab jo chahata hai peda kerta hai aur jisay chahata hai chun leta hai inn mein say kissi ko koi ikhtiyar nahi Allah hi kay liye paki hai woh buland tar hai her uss cheez say kay log shareek kertay hain
  28,69,Unn kay seenay jo kuch chupatay aur jo kuch zahir kertay hain aap ka rab sab kuch janta hai
  28,70,Wohi Allah hai uss kay siwa koi laeeq-e-ibadat nahi duniya aur aakhirat mein ussi ki tareef hai. Ussi kay liye farman rawaqee hai aur ussi ki taraf tum sab pheray jao gay
  28,71,Keh dijiye! kay dekho to sahi agar Allah Taalaa tum per raat hi raat qayamat tak barabar ker dey to siwaye Allah kay kaun mabood hai jo tumharay pass din ki roshni laye? Kiya tum suntay nahi ho
  28,72,Poochiye! Kay yeh bhi batado kay agar Allah Taalaa tum per hamesha qayamat tak din hi din rakhay to bhi siwaye Allah Taalaa kay koi mabood hai jo tumharay pass raat ley aaye? Jiss mein tum aaraam hasil kero kiya tum dekh nahi rahey ho
  28,73,Ussi ney tumharay liye apnay fazal-o-karam say din raat muqarrar ker diye hain kay tum raat mein aaraam kero aur din mein uss ki bheji hui rozi talash kero yeh iss liye kay tum shukar ada kero
  28,74,Aur jiss din unhen pukar ker Allah Taalaa farmaye ga jinhen tum meray shareek khayal kertay thay woh kahan hain
  28,75,Aur hum her ummat mein say aik gawah alag ker len gay kay apni daleelen paish kero pus uss waqt jaan len gay kay haq Allah Taalaa ki taraf hai aur jo kuch iftra woh jortay thay sab unn kay pass say kho jaye ga